<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="dark">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <title>Bot Dashboard</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <script>(function(){try{document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme',localStorage.getItem('theme')||'dark')}catch(e){}})()</script>
</head>
<body><div class="page-wrapper">

<nav class="navbar"><div class="nav-inner">
  <a href="/" class="nav-brand"><span class="nav-logo">⚡</span><span class="nav-name">tedisanxd</span></a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="/" class="nav-link active">Home</a>
    <a href="/commands" class="nav-link">Commands</a>
    <a href="/status" class="nav-link">Status</a>
    <a href="/roadmap" class="nav-link">Roadmap</a>
    <a href="/suggestions" class="nav-link">Suggestions</a>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-right">
    <div class="theme-switcher">
      <button class="theme-btn" id="themeToggle" title="Change theme">🎨</button>
      <div class="theme-dropdown" id="themeDropdown">
        <div class="theme-option" data-theme="dark">🌙 Dark</div>
        <div class="theme-option" data-theme="amoled">⚫ AMOLED</div>
        <div class="theme-option" data-theme="midnight">🌌 Midnight</div>
        <div class="theme-option" data-theme="slate">💜 Slate</div>
        <div class="theme-option" data-theme="light">☀️ Light</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <% if (user) { %>
      <div class="nav-user">
        <img class="nav-avatar" src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/<%= user.id %>/<%= user.avatar %>.png?size=64" alt="">
        <span class="nav-username"><%= user.username %></span>
      </div>
      <a href="/guilds" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">My Servers</a>
      <a href="/auth/logout" class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm">Logout</a>
    <% } else { %>
      <a href="/auth/discord" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Login with Discord</a>
    <% } %>
  </div>
</div></nav>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-badge">⚡ by tedisanxd</div>
  <h1>Manage Your<br><span class="gradient-text">Discord Server</span></h1>
  <p>A full-featured moderation bot by <strong style="color:var(--text)">tedisanxd</strong> — AutoMod, logging, XP, verification and more, all from one dashboard.</p>
  <div class="hero-buttons">
    <% if (user) { %>
      <a href="/guilds" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Go to Dashboard →</a>
    <% } else { %>
      <a href="/auth/discord" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Login with Discord</a>
    <% } %>
    <a href="/status" class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg">View Status</a>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-stats">
    <div class="hero-stat"><div class="hero-stat-value"><%= stats.guilds %></div><div class="hero-stat-label">Servers</div></div>
    <div class="hero-stat"><div class="hero-stat-value"><%= stats.users %></div><div class="hero-stat-label">Users</div></div>
    <div class="hero-stat"><div class="hero-stat-value"><%= stats.cases %></div><div class="hero-stat-label">Mod Actions</div></div>
    <div class="hero-stat"><div class="hero-stat-value"><% if(stats.online){%><span class="text-success">Online</span><%}else{%><span class="text-danger">Offline</span><%}%></div><div class="hero-stat-label">Status</div></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="features-section">
  <div class="features-title">Everything you need</div>
  <div class="features-sub">A full-featured bot with all the tools to run a professional server.</div>
  <div class="features">
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon">🔨</div><h3>Moderation Suite</h3><p>Ban, kick, mute, timeout and warn. Full case tracking with mod logs.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon">🤖</div><h3>AutoMod</h3><p>Detect spam, bad words, invite links and URLs. Fully configurable.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon">📋</div><h3>Event Logging</h3><p>Log every server event across dedicated channels. Toggle per event type.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon">🛡️</div><h3>Ban Evasion Detection</h3><p>Track banned users by ID. Auto-ban known evaders and flag new accounts.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon">⭐</div><h3>XP & Levels</h3><p>Engage your community with XP, leaderboards and level-up messages.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon">🎭</div><h3>Reaction Roles</h3><p>Let members self-assign roles by reacting to messages.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon">👋</div><h3>Welcome Messages</h3><p>Greet new members with custom messages and variable substitution.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon">🏷️</div><h3>Custom Commands</h3><p>Create tag commands for FAQs and server info — anyone can use them.</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

<footer><div class="footer-inner">
  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text-secondary)"><span style="font-size:18px">⚡</span> Dashboard</div>
  <div class="footer-links"><a href="/commands">Commands</a><a href="/status">Status</a><a href="/roadmap">Roadmap</a><a href="/suggestions">Suggestions</a><a href="/license">License</a></div>
  <div style="color:var(--muted)">© 2025 tedisanxd. All rights reserved.</div>
</div></footer>

<script src="/js/app.js"></script>
</div></body></html>
